{"tid":1329193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[又送到入更衣室] 送禮勤賽後報告 Round 2","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T23:58:04.000Z","uid":39752,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"643608e941d31403899dbb19feda66f8188a8693","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">首先感謝大家對送禮勤咁支持</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHvA3Hz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHvA3Hz.jpg&h=8eb8fe2b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n講緊唔只各位金主同埋連登仔／CD-ROM，重有各位五毛、三毛、同埋一班慕名而來嘅大陸朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為咗保持低調我都唔 link 返舊 post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">講返事發經過先</span></strong></span><br />\n我哋完全估唔到上次會有咁多人留意，又有好多連登仔／CD-ROM 幫手廣傳，消息遠到第二日食飯就有完全唔上連登嘅朋友問起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱我哋又發生咗啲技術故障* 熄唔到個 group invite，結果就係我哋極速截咗捐款，但人就不斷湧入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦好坦白講不乏各種三毛五毛，然後傳傳吓連一啲真係關心緊香港情況嘅大陸朋友都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋送禮勤搞手一致認為，經過幾次行動同埋連登個 post 傳得太遠，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">送禮勤已經開始高調，往後嘅行動資訊要更加保密</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我哋而家喺個公海 group 度交代嘅嘢好少，所有願意出嚟派嘢嘅送禮勤、加工部嘅奴工、金主等等全部已經有獨立群組，公海個 group 只會用嚟招募新嘅送禮勤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n* 技術故障就係某個 admin 無 revoke 條 link&hellip;&hellip;我哋已經處理咗佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SgZ2JP8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSgZ2JP8.jpg&h=76fc58ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>金流情況</strong></span></span><br />\n1. <strong>我哋極速籌咗超過一萬蚊，然後就己經停咗收錢</strong><br />\n2. 所有金主都已經加入獨立群組接收我哋嘅行動計劃同匯報<br />\n3. 舊有嘅財務報告連結仍然有效，不過唔知會計 admin 收齊啲單執完支出記錄未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋立場係絕對支持大家各有各做開多十檔出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但請留意現階段任何課金買禮物嘅籌款都同送禮勤無關</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">製作方面點？</span></span></strong><br />\n我哋已經為之後嘅行動整咗全新設計同禮物形式，費事你哋認得，講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另外在此鳴謝一啲表示可以免費提供禮品製作服務嘅巴打絲打</span></strong>，但係我哋唔希望受人免費幫忙，希望大家都係用返現買現賣、對成個行動更好更安全嘅合作模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有能力嘅不妨自己開多一檔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">行動效果？</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 我哋有追蹤上水同沙田兩次行動嘅數據，轉換率比普通實體廣告高四至五倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />證明關心嘅人真係唔少<br />\n2. 不過最勁嘅係，根據其中一個 admin 消息，大陸已經有人出 post 叫人「去香港唔好亂咁接人派嘅嘢」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">下一輪行動？</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 我哋已經同提供到新文宣內容嘅朋友溝通緊，新嘅禮物會有更龐大嘅資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 因為沙田同上水兩次行動都出現咗意料之外嘅危險（黑狗我屌你老母死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行都未撚行完就開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），加上資金相對充足，我哋跟住落嚟嘅行動會有以下方針<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;　我哋照樣會喺各個遊行時段出現，但會改為派較為輕便易走佬嘅傳單<br />\n&mdash;　<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>遍地開花，區區有禮送</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次都講過如果資金充裕就唔會再玩死一個時間地點，歡迎大家提出各種新奇有創意嘅送禮地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 721 唔會有送禮勤，大家一齊推好隻 boss 佢！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請見字所有巴打絲打注意安全！<br />\n快啲買裝！快啲買急救包！721 見！</span></strong></span><br />\n麥麥加推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人人都可以學急救知識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1322903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1322903/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5a1b5a632739bc4db2ac52640a2c39d68d9c6924","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"係咪今次太低調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92341114486326905be6d9a11f5b5c156aab882","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4f92661ec9195e3227e75c6ff51bbb78feeb5b","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae57d406e8b33ced87be0053407e5d10b78378f","tid":1329193,"uid":128509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fa94e2e22b1ceedf1cfbc0e0c663da309fbcd08","tid":1329193,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"[721]彩彈戰術風格，實測報告<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324287</a><br />\n<br />\n【遊戲更新：終極裝備攻略】我在香城Online 2.0 等你～～<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RvjxAU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RvjxAU</a><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂][精簡篇]裝備及防火須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321549</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【 速報】《中英聯合聲明》眾籌備戰情況<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RxoKcU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RxoKcU</a><br />\n<br />\n［最終設計]黑警有旗手 我哋都有旗手 麻煩各位可以自製<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djFtqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djFtqS</a><br />\n<br />\n[721 廣傳] 兄弟爬山 對抗暴徒 物資採購攻略 - Decathlon<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324768</a>"},{"pid":"3ed1cebbc97b9f72a86f7cd993d852db70f60fd6","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdaee9ae0a526ff16bce013d84f7c7b25e135e9","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a734777428778abaca356a7911ecec01d628c1","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9509960ad1b11047d514971ec037c47ca5c81dbe","tid":1329193,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f1839922d8b7db15798a52aca13da50248fb8f","tid":1329193,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0d77c728d3f605ec2a6b422705b47abfa68ff5","tid":1329193,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"ed11244c808d1ae6af6200da2b3da4d3fd50200b","tid":1329193,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T